# Phase labeling

When expanding VMS template or intake fields, label work explicitly:

| Phase | Goal |
|-------|------|
| **A** | Map existing collected data to template tags (`docxBuilder` only) |
| **B** | Add intake UI + DB + PATCH for high-value missing fields |
| **C** | Enrich via Gemini parse + resume text for snapshot/experience blocks |

Do not add template tags without a data source plan. Prefer shipping A before B, B before C.

State which phase a PR covers in title or description.
